profile_positions.description:
As senior researcher/business developer at Erasmus Centre for Urban, Port & Transport Economics I focus on two main themes:

1) conduct action research projects on how ports and port-cities can be developed sustainably, thereby striking a balance between economic and societal values;

2) develop educational products and provide training solutions that support port and maritime professionals around the world in better comprehending how to deal with wicked problems that ports and their port-cities are facing while striving for balanced and inclusive growth.
